Cyber Claw:




It was not much Cyber Claw could resort to. She always relied on 
herself to get through things. She was going to rely on her mind to 
get her to this new plan, and settle herself down, keep a low 
profile. 

Something finally clicked. That one bot at the new Predacon base 
sounded welcoming to her, even sounded like he wanted her to stay. 
That is if she felt like it. Bug-boy didn't like her. She could 
settle down there until she could figure out what the Vok wanted.

She followed her nose and navagational systems and walked on, towards 
the position of the Typicon (Being terrible today with writing. 
Forgive me.)
